WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:08.990 --> 00:00:12.120
Hi everyone Chinese New Year
is only a few days away

00:00:12.120 --> 00:00:16.260
today I'm going to make a very
traditional Sichuan dish whole fish

00:00:16.260 --> 00:00:21.650
in bean paste this is a must have dish at my
family's Chinese New Year's Eve dinner

00:00:21.650 --> 00:00:26.320
Fish in Chinese, Yui, has the same pronunciation as abundance

00:00:26.320 --> 00:00:31.440
Whole fish symbolizes a year of abundance
and good luck

00:00:31.440 --> 00:00:34.500
here are the ingredients

00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:44.360
of one whole fish, tilapia, and it's about 2 pounds we need scallion, ginger, garlic

00:00:44.360 --> 00:00:55.260
spicy bean paste, I chopped it finely
sugar, salt, soy sauce Chinese cooking

00:00:55.260 --> 00:01:03.120
wine, vinegar, canola oil and also wet starch

00:01:03.120 --> 00:01:05.940
before cooking we chopped up

00:01:05.940 --> 00:01:12.140
scallions, ginger and garlic for the fish
dry the fish with paper towel make three

00:01:12.140 --> 00:01:20.340
cuts on both sides put salt on and also
inside the fish we are ready to cook

00:01:22.180 --> 00:01:26.000
first let's pan fry the fish

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:29.220
put a little bit of oil

00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:35.080
let's put the fish in

00:01:37.420 --> 00:01:42.960
pan fry about two minutes each side

00:01:43.060 --> 00:01:47.560
okay let's flip the fish

00:01:49.520 --> 00:01:54.340
cook the other side for another two minutes

00:01:56.560 --> 00:02:02.280
after about two minutes let's take out the fish

00:02:09.060 --> 00:02:14.160
add some oil to the pan

00:02:17.320 --> 00:02:25.860
add ginger, garlic

00:02:27.460 --> 00:02:31.460
bean paste

00:02:35.420 --> 00:02:38.700
sugar

00:02:48.900 --> 00:02:53.700
we'll also add a little bit of vinegar

00:02:56.650 --> 00:02:59.610
soy sauce

00:03:01.890 --> 00:03:04.850
cooking wine

00:03:09.160 --> 00:03:12.030
mix it up

00:03:17.140 --> 00:03:21.040
now let's add the water

00:03:24.990 --> 00:03:28.910
enough to cover the fish

00:03:30.830 --> 00:03:33.700
let it boil

00:03:36.030 --> 00:03:41.900
now the water is boiling let's put the fish back

00:03:47.210 --> 00:03:52.220
scoop some of the sauce on

00:04:00.099 --> 00:04:05.730
cover it,  cook about eight to ten minutes

00:04:07.650 --> 00:04:14.030
so occasionally scoop the sauce on top of the fish

00:04:17.850 --> 00:04:20.870
and let it cook

00:04:24.870 --> 00:04:30.199
after about eight minutes, the fish is done

00:04:31.940 --> 00:04:39.620
put some sauce on, let's take out the fish

00:04:47.200 --> 00:04:54.240
okay now let's add scallions in

00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:09.000
last let's add the wet starch

00:05:15.980 --> 00:05:18.860
mixed it up

00:05:19.500 --> 00:05:22.680
and we're going to pour the sauce on the fish

00:05:22.680 --> 00:05:25.680
we are ready to serve

00:05:37.980 --> 00:05:42.200
then we garnish with scallions

00:05:44.620 --> 00:05:47.380
whole fish in bean paste

00:05:47.380 --> 00:05:50.300
Wish everybody very Happy Chinese New Year

00:05:50.300 --> 00:05:51.680
the year of the dragon

00:05:51.680 --> 00:05:55.140
wish you a lot of luck, happiness and health!

00:05:55.140 --> 00:05:57.980
thank you for watching

